  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4e736ff2-3ca4-4376-ac05-c590cd6aa6cb\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b> 판촉물</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6f28672-6315-49f2-a10d-442dc15caef9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223869523988/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">부채 주문 방법</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c1f0300-b73c-45a0-9ef8-7ea17c0eb783\" style=\"color:#555555;\">부채는 7가지의 모양으로 만들 수 있습니다.  원과 사각형, 그리고 물결 또는 하트나 별 모양입니다. 모양이 필요하신 분은 문의하시면 모양 칼선을 별도로 보내드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-85c239d8-43ea-4053-8d75-0c8b8d1d1e50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00555fc7-6712-4590-83f7-6abc7151276f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b48ebe26-ce51-436e-b2c1-0028fa90f59c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a7c0e43-bfab-4f6f-a1ad-2a9a38a3548f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 이 종이부채는 소량으로 생산되므로 하나의 종이와 규격으로만 주문이 가능합니다. 양면인쇄가 기본이고 코팅도 반드시 해야 되는 제품입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7320e7e1-1959-4d38-abaa-a5d1fe48fab3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47f3d253-4e14-4149-8f5a-781bb18c13ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b06e3298-8a1c-48b6-8429-5ccd01a41720\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c11699fd-2ede-4c80-bcc2-3620378dffd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 디지털 커팅으로 소량 제작되므로 약간의 뜯김이 발생될 수 있으나 제품에는 전혀 하자가 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9aff4ac-b75c-4a06-a442-4831da5aa6fa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-67a3c0d8-84c0-4706-8271-faa60edf878b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-694b8208-c6a4-4c43-8efd-a89dce482708\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-83a2707b-3003-469d-aaad-b37e1ed13c5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>진행 과정은 다음과 같습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce4e6439-1308-4692-9841-336aea86dedb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7014da70-702b-4bce-b9fb-add5142a5293\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c471665a-5107-4e4d-968b-eb5704965c3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a04815e-b99b-4f91-9130-96edb483c1d3\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">견적요청</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6763e0f0-f9ef-4c84-bd8b-6c9ff6d4c9b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2249609-2e59-4cd9-85ce-ebfbbaa5b36d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">칼선 전달</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62f8dd58-58ff-47cc-8adf-d0b2be591573\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba07ba74-6b3f-40ce-be1c-3a89343f505f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디자인 파일 발주</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5739a758-8d8a-4e04-9295-92bf02ee2cbe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2fb72635-8f24-42ed-87e9-e2122db2d08a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">입금</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14a67359-7f20-4633-b186-65f18e74bbc3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bada4e85-5e3e-49e6-88ec-3f1746f840ad\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디자인 검증</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5973e3bd-5c5c-487f-9050-2e7448d9a18f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fac4f2c8-a1ff-4c2a-9a2d-eda443c33703\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">디자인 파일 컨펌</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-274df202-69d4-4628-a95e-29b4d2f12ff4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87798789-872a-4000-a4c7-7a10882acf58\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">생산</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1863f82d-4696-4c55-bac9-ff5bc4b52b5c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-560cf196-b7cf-4aee-8d41-bc5082b89b21\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">배송 완료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04e6d31c-02bf-4a9e-a2fa-a5d7036e93d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aeb4adbb-1132-4319-b85a-c3194d0e3dd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c217c874-ea9d-45fa-bfcb-d3b0483849dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9972ff9-7a85-47ec-8a73-b774abe6ecf4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">처음으로 하셔야 하는 것이 견적을 요청하는 작업입니다. 종이부채는 형태와 수량이 중요합니다. 형태와 수량을 주시면 칼선과 견적서를 제출해 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b7bce38-6eab-4b64-bdb1-393461098106\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1741256-5a5e-42d8-9882-45afaf2b71a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b5bf802-d6e8-455a-b286-314aa2b400b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b04d7f20-be6e-4ffe-b644-8f7b9106e171\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저희가 드리는 견적이 마음에 드시면 디자인 작업 후에 입금과 함께 디자인 파일을 전달해 주십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1557f4f4-269a-4eea-aa2a-a6f52489e213\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4d5ecae-f128-48bb-b3d8-922902826cff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a63d56a0-bd78-45ab-9182-f4f8e3c61aa1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0950fca4-39b5-4194-ae3b-d462a7ddd666\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인 파일을 전달받으면 입금계좌와 디자인 파일 점검 후에 컨펌 작업을 진행합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6849b30d-0f13-4507-8841-5a506c60bcc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e876885e-8303-4756-8f1f-a8e19e497f73\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92cdbe84-1a76-4101-a971-36e12236536f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1a7ec62-9d6b-4a86-b8c1-ae1636c9d38e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">컨펌이 되면 생산이 되고 합의된 배송 방법으로 물건을 전달해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d940bfed-2142-4806-94c4-55cd38636681\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ace626b3-7756-44ac-9968-069669541767\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbc986d9-7026-4876-925a-d345d7439efe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a7436a8d-a39d-41f9-9345-57122be5fb9d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이후 완료하고 저희와 소통 후 마무리하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-57a86047-00df-4316-9de3-95c1284be605\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f8cb7f9-0826-4de1-9d38-20aac221bb0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-52ed033a-61b3-4bdd-97a5-30bd8d6e50fd\" style=\"\">종이부채 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3304dc12-7449-4cc6-88b4-0dc79f630a85\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ae3dac1-e494-4f8c-8179-7f4c3ca41147\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bc41bf8b-1c4e-4912-a6f5-473f2bd41cd3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-000892db-fcde-440b-b7af-da18751372ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반지 350g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7134bf03-6924-4b62-898e-22d859f6f774\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-909dac58-7391-441c-a987-c915c22186bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65654cea-b0ae-4fad-82e9-56a990d084fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 190mm × 190mm 이내 (형태에 따라 약간 달라집니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e86ba57-5526-42f9-a67a-fc9f266771db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f49da0c1-d416-4201-99f2-067675fb6171\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e96f80b-ced2-4a9e-a689-e012f289481d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면 컬러 CMYK 인쇄 기본</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-374eb67a-6aae-4e97-b38c-e4af7c3238b9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e2e628c5-c984-42b9-a229-f432a2b9c868\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6caa7dde-209a-4571-8634-9b32a4f93658\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면 무광코팅 기본</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65cc6509-b762-411b-9504-eb75723b92c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-966f62e2-2288-47cb-965a-c0b6c83a96ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03c215a1-a8bf-4946-91c7-16eb257fa103\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 디지털 커팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-975764f9-8040-4196-b495-b037af7d0faf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f861e122-b4a5-4c42-ad03-aec037d6e0b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>최소 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7c9b291-f973-4235-ac16-e0c67a15cbca\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 6개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd077db0-c624-4b75-aa05-272f999ebb0d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb6baeca-622b-4982-8694-7df4e9724ef0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f1fe602-4d29-4dc5-8eed-c1f116aad67b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39b5ed99-34ef-44dc-8487-4ddd8e8d7b42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 더워지는 계절이 왔습니다. 부채는 전통적으로 가장 좋은 판촉물 중에 하나입니다. 행사나 기타 선물용으로 멋지게 디자인하여 소량으로 생산하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95a9e260-9f39-4236-959a-f689c52d8efb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-469638e0-a913-4c16-adc6-4f9ba5bb317b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62f86d8d-ae49-43a8-873b-582d0ac1182f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-766158df-82e7-4950-a66e-210611a59a15\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">고객의 성장을 의해 최선을 다하겠습니다. 항상 노력하는 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f14a2b1b-5ca4-4f8c-a6a6-8349411d3666\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd29e47c-9aac-4c03-bbcc-db403aad8a23\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba455990-cec9-47db-ab79-8f6c4ecae518\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d0a77f3-c77a-4e9c-afa1-f6e6579f6781\" style=\"color:#555555;\">최고의 디자이너가 함께합니다. 디자인 작업까지 의뢰하시면 보다 좋은 혜택을 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c354f78a-2370-4eed-ad68-1e1d4a853231\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38358267-03dc-4660-bed4-ca2b073e0f17\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
